# This repository is PUBLIC.
#
# It exists for ONE reason: Buffer fetches post images from a public URL at
# posting time, so finished cards must be reachable on the open internet.
#
# Only rendered card images belong here. Nothing sourced from a coaching call,
# no transcripts, no notes, no drafts, no client material of any kind.
# The denylist below blocks everything by default and re-admits PNGs only.

*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!cards/
!cards/**/
!cards/**/*.png
